  <main>
        
            <img width="2047" height="984" src="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-sand-from-ice.jpg" class="singlepostthumb wp-post-image" alt="iceberg" decoding="async" srcset="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-sand-from-ice.jpg 2047w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-sand-from-ice-520x250.jpg 520w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-sand-from-ice-1200x577.jpg 1200w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-sand-from-ice-768x369.jpg 768w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-sand-from-ice-1536x738.jpg 1536w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-sand-from-ice-900x433.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 2047px) 100vw, 2047px" /><div class="post-thumbnail-caption">An iceberg floats in Disko Bay, near Ilulissat, Greenland. The country’s massive ice sheet is shedding about 300 gigatonnes of ice a year into the ocean, making it the single largest source of sea level rise from melting ice. Photo by NASA/Saskia Madlener/Flickr</div>      <article class="main container col4">
                <header class="maincol">
                    <h1 class="pagetitle">Greenland’s Melting Ice Sheet Brings an Unexpected Flow of Wealth Potential</h1>
                    <h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Greenlanders are largely in favor of extracting the sand pouring from their melting ice sheet, as long as Greenland reaps the rewards.</h2>
                    <section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
            <h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
            by  
                    <a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/moira-donovan/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Moira Donovan</a>                <br/>
                        </section>
           
          <aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
            <h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
            November 3, 2022 | 1,500 words, about 7 minutes          </aside>
        </header>

        <aside class="shareicons">
          <h3 class="invis">Share this article</h3>
                              <p>Share this:</p>
          <ul>
            <!-- <li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share" href="mailto:?&subject=Check%20out%20this%20site!&body=https://hakaimagazine.com/features/greenlands-melting-ice-sheet-brings-an-unexpected-flow-of-wealth-potential/%20-%20Greenlanders+are+largely+in+favor+of+extracting+the+sand+pouring+from+their+melting+ice+sheet%2C+as+long+as+Greenland+reaps+the+rewards.%0A"><span>Share using email</span></a></li> -->
            <li><a class="icons icon-flipboard tagmanager" id="share_flipboard_top" href="https://share.flipboard.com/bookmarklet/popout?v=2&title=Greenland’s Melting Ice Sheet Brings an Unexpected Flow of Wealth Potential&url=https%3A%2F%2Fhakaimagazine.com%2Ffeatures%2Fgreenlands-melting-ice-sheet-brings-an-unexpected-flow-of-wealth-potential%2F"><span>Share on Flipboard</span></a></li>
